  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a sha256 content hash is recorded but the digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending reviewer approval. All 13 credibility factors are addressed. Package is submitted as Accepted pending signature completion.",
